model

Class TableColumn

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.TableColumn

  • public class TableColumn
extends java.lang.Object
    Class representing a column of a TableSchema. It contains all metadata for one column. That includes data as name, code, size and references to JsonNode from the TreeModel and TableSchema.
    Author:
    Milan Radeta
